creator: LR Studios
descriptionHtml:
Fill-in Crosswords (also known as Fill-it-ins or Word Fills) is a popular word game similar to crosswords.

Fill-in puzzles are a variation of the common crossword puzzle in which words, rather than clues, are given.

Features :
- Several levels of difficulty, from beginner to very hard
- A mix of crossword grid styles : american, french, italian, ... (the difference is in the way the black squares are placed)
- 2 new puzzles every day
- Several languages available
- Many settings to customize the features and the look and feel of the grid
descriptionShort: Fill in the crossword grid with the given words. Simple and relaxing!

creator: LR Studios
descriptionHtml:
Fill-In Crosswords (also known as Fill-Ins) is a fun variation of the classic crossword puzzle: instead of clues, your goal is to fill in the grid with the given words. However, there is only one possible solution!

The app comes with hundreds of free fill-in puzzles ranging from beginner to expert. Plus, tackle our daily puzzles to keep your mind sharp and your vocabulary growing! 📚

⭐ Discover new words and improve your vocabulary
⭐ Play offline without a connection, whenever you want
⭐ Easy to play with a simple and clear design
⭐ Daily puzzles to train your brain
⭐ Choose between simple and relaxing puzzles or more challenging ones
⭐ You can play with or without a timer, if you prefer a more relax mode
⭐ 2,000+ puzzles with difficulties for everyone
⭐ 8 supported languages (with more to come)
⭐ Improve your word and spelling skills
⭐ Use hints if you get stuck

With daily puzzles available, you can make fill-in puzzles part of your daily routine to keep your mind sharp. The game offers both easy and hard puzzles, allowing you to choose your level of challenge. It's a perfect way to relax while also expanding your knowledge.

Fill-ins is a brain-teasing game that combines the fun of crossword games with fill-in challenges! Whether you're a crossword enthusiast or just enjoy word games, the app offers an exciting way to discover new words and improve your vocabulary and spelling.

Unlike classic crosswords, Fill-ins don't require extensive knowledge, making it enjoyable for everyone. It's a great way to train your brain, improve your vocabulary and spelling, and have fun with words! It's also a free game that you can enjoy anytime, anywhere, even offline!
descriptionShort: Simple and relaxing, these puzzles will help you improve your vocabulary!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Multiple bugfixes
- Button to view daily puzzle stats (total solved, best time, ...)
- 2 new "Numbers" puzzle packs
